description: Bosch Wagner has gone to see the doctor, Justin Cade.  Since Bosch is already stripped down to his boxers it only seems right that Justin disrobe also.  Bosch's tongue goes right for the good doctor's ass while nurse Scott O'Hara looks through a crack in the door.  This doctor is well equipped and Bosch has more than a mouthful.  Scott comes in and Bosch is more than happy to satisfy the nurse as well as the doctor.
title: In Your Wildest Dreams, Scene #04
